// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7182 — Mass File Rename (brotherhood)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 3b013a99-c59f-5605-9573-226d97ae6b59

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
